{"type": "article", "id": 28181, "title": "耐克下一位合作者来自 LV，它和 Liberty 的合作球鞋也很好看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-14T10:45:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 28948, "name": "Fenty"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 1190, "name": "伦敦男装周"}, {"id": 16820, "name": "艺术总监"}, {"id": 8279, "name": "合作"}, {"id": 6132, "name": "加拿大"}, {"id": 548, "name": "快时尚"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 14857, "name": "Clarks"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 28949, "name": "F21 Red"}, {"id": 3530, "name": "Forever 21"}, {"id": 7207, "name": "Eddie Redmayne"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 21942, "name": "Kim Jones"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162440LEPG0rYhDtWNB2sJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><b><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/nike-louis-vuitton-kim-jones-collection\">Nike 将与 LV 男装艺术总监合作</a></b>｜继发布与 Balmain 创意总监 Olivier Rousteing  的合作系列后，Nike 近日又宣布将与 Louis Vuitton 男装艺术总监 Kim Jones 合作，具体细节还未透露，预计发布日期在今年七月。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Clarks-annual-profits-worse-than-expected-drop-by-65-,702824.html\"><b>Clarks 年利润逊预期</b></a>｜英国鞋履品牌 Clarks 截至 2016 年 1 月 31 日的营业利润出现显著下跌，从 1.127 亿英镑下滑至 4580 万英镑，尽管期间营业额有 2.6% 的上涨。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Quebec-to-welcome-first-ever-F21-Red-store,702912.html\"><b>F21 Red 在魁北克开首家店</b></a>｜F21 Red 为快时尚品牌 Forever 21 旗下低价概念店，近日宣布秋季将在加拿大魁北克开第一家店，14667 平方英尺的店内将售卖 Forever 21 全品类，包括 Forever 21、Forever 21 Men、Forever 21 Plus、和 Forever 21 Kids。F21 Red 于去年秋季进驻加拿大，新店将是全加第四家。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Nike-partners-with-China-s-Ministry-of-Education,702914.html\"><b>Nike 与教育部合作</b></a>｜Nike 将于我国教育部合作，通过在小学发展体育教育课程以提高国内超过两百万儿童的健康水平，将在 300 余所学校帮助 7000 名以上的体育教师接受培训。Nike 总裁兼 CEO Mark Parker 表示此项行动为中美文化交流的一部分。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>Prada 在官方 Instagram 账号上透露，<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/31557/1/eddie-redmayne-is-the-new-face-of-prada\">Eddie Redmayne 为其拍摄最新男装大片</a>（2016 秋冬）。顺便一提，这些照片看上去也太不小雀斑了，有一种装腔作势的感觉。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162414f9y7X0oYChgG4q8S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162415MbwktlpRu8sAGg2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66793893\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162415gU96liLwa0Vkxq1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162416lAoZn2reb9NujcXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rihanna-fenty-puma-release-new-trainer-color-way-10454592/\">Alexander McQueen 2017 春夏男装</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021624175Azqmk32sgef9H1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021624188jBZpc1kEzhnKNIs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162419omTRC3EVJet6vjwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162419t6k04hni8yjYvKem.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021624210lcxu5AVJW4jvnrB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162421tMpl9xv4ahbLW8c5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162422qhtsrJvFKVTwQO51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rihanna-fenty-puma-release-new-trainer-color-way-10454592/\">Rihanna 的 Fenty 鞋系列释出新配色</a>，灰色版本售价预计在 180 美元。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162422X0bzceKVIhYOQo5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/london/coach/fashion-scoops/\">Coach 亮相伦敦男装周</a>，其中的女模揭示了中性风格，采用“即看即买”模式：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162423vTRoim0eYDApXtbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162423pXEfF6z5SOxKq0Ne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162426C7OJDSsT9rUKguEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162427VqjCJrNsLHelpgIE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162428ZcT4OWM3i95lVFCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162433ZYv6zwOEcBjod5Fh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">英伦经典品牌 Liberty 以印花出名，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/nikecourt-liberty-collection\">近日推出与 NikeCourt 的合作系列</a>，夏日花卉印花元素为主：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021624337nOHaXugPloQ9szV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162434J4ZojHvClfQ3gzis.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162434c2drhkUHuAvpCVnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162435PybIdVYweAnLiNlh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162435x8VtZP2YAp3HQqkF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/stone-island-2016-fall-winter-collection\">意大利科技服饰 Stone Island 秋冬系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162436H9dghVWnfzrMktPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162437Nrn6LuxySb24ciAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162438yVrRcgfAlD2dnmiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162438tQMxbe6TPJvNI1yu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162439Fn7KcYg5RQZE1BUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\